		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>See: @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.equipment24.Item.dmgIounStone0000]{Ioun Stone}</em></p><p>When you take a Action to toss an <em>Ioun Stone</em> into the air, the stone orbits your head at a distance of 1d3 feet, conferring its benefit to you while doing so. You can have up to three <em>Ioun Stones</em> orbiting your head at the same time.</p><p>As a Utilize action, you can seize and stow any number of <em>Ioun Stones</em> orbiting your head. If your Attunement to an <em>Ioun Stone</em> ends while it's orbiting your head, the stone falls as though you had dropped it.</p><p><span>Your Charisma increases by 2, to a maximum of 20, while this marbled pink and green sphere orbits your head.</span></p>",
